'''Shayzien armour (5)''' is a set of [[armour]] that requires 20 [[Defence]] to wear. In order to receive tier 5 Shayzien armour, players must have 100% Shayzien favour and own all pieces of [[Shayzien armour 4|tier 4 Shayzien armour]]. Its defence bonuses are between [[steel armour]] and [[black armour]].

'''Note:''' Players may destroy any pieces of Shayzien armour they have acquired. But to fight higher tier [[Soldier (tier 5)|soldiers]] again player must have full set of armour that is no more than 1 tier lower than that soldier.

It is dropped by the [[Soldier (tier 5)|tier 5 soldier]] at the [[Combat Ring (Shayzien)|Combat Ring]] in [[Shayzien]]. Players must kill the soldier 5 times in order to receive all the pieces.

The set also protects players from the poison attack of the [[lizardman shaman]]. This effect is increased per added piece, with each piece giving around a 1/5th damage reduction, capping at a full 100% damage reduction with all 5 pieces.

